
Create a rollover effect that can change the color of its text.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Rollover Effect - Easiest Way</title>
<style>
.rollover-text {
color: #333;
cursor: pointer;
}
.rollover-text:hover {
color: #ff6347;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Hover over the text to see the rollover effect (Easiest Way)</h2>
<!-- Text with rollover effect -->
<p class="rollover-text">This text will change color on hover.</p>
</body>
</html>
